dataStructure.name: sid.org.tmforum.tip.resource.res.log.tip.nrf.FloatingTerminationPoint
dataStructure.description:
This object class represents a TP without a physical layer that behaves both like a PTP and a CTP. Floating Termination Points (FTPs) are contained in managed elements as PTPs. Note: The value of tpMappingMode for FTPs considers exclusively mapping on the server side. See R_TMF518_NRF_I_0011.

This entity is optional

This entity is extendable

This entity generates Object Creation notifications

This entity generates Object Deletion notifications

This entity generates Object Discovery notifications
dataStructure.label: FloatingTerminationPoint
